# --- AI agent state & per-CLI context adapters -------------------------------
# This repo's portable, CLI-agnostic AI layer is .ai/ (skills + rules.md) and
# AGENTS.md (the cross-tool context file every modern agent reads). Each CLI's
# own working dir / local config / session data is tool-specific and may hold
# PII — transcripts, history, credentials, file paths — so it is never committed.
# Per-CLI context files (CLAUDE.md, etc.) are generated locally from AGENTS.md;
# the deliberate Claude dotfile *sources* live in claude/ (tracked) instead.
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
AGENTS.local.md
.cursor/
.copilot/
.aider*
.continue/
.codeium/
.windsurf/
.gemini/
.qwen/

# Secrets / credentials
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.secret
